|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|3       |124         |
|2 |  └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |3       |121         |
|3 |    └─TABLE RANGE SCAN   |t1(idx1)|3       |121         |
=============================================================
